          <title>Minnesota U.S. Attorney Andy Luger to step down ahead of Trump transition</title>
          <description><![CDATA[U.S. Attorney Andy Luger is stepping down soon as the top federal law enforcement official in Minnesota. As is custom for political appointees, he’s resigning to make way for a yet-to-be-announced successor chosen by incoming President Donald Trump.]]></description>
